        "benefits": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Benefits",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "ol_list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list_item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Beneficiary: Mother/Father/Natural guardian"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list_item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "The child gets health insurance coverage up to a maximum of Rs. 25,000 a year."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list_item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "The annual scholarship of Rs. 300 to Rs. 1,000 up to the tenth standard is given to the girl"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list_item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "To Promote the birth of girl children in economically weaker families and to raise their status within the family and society."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list_item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "To provide Financial assistance to the girl child through her mother/father/natural guardian subject to the fulfilment of certain conditions"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list_item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Apart from these benefits, the parents have got Rs. 1 lakh in case of an accident and Rs. 42,500 for the natural death of the beneficiary. At the end of 18 years, the beneficiary would be paid Rs.34, 751."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list_item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Certain interim payments such as annual scholarships and insurance benefits have made available to the beneficiary on continued fulfilment of the eligibility criteria"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "bold": true,
                    "text": ""
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "bold": true,
                "text": "The annual scholarship amount for Bhagya Laxmi Scheme is given in the table below:"
