      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "**Eligibility**\n\n1. A girl’s birth must be registered within a year after her birth date.\n1. Girls shouldn’t engage in child labour.\n1. Benefits from the Bhagyalakshmi scheme are available to BPL families with up to 2 female children.\n1. Girls should have been immunized correctly in the health department’s program.\n1. Girl children must be born after 31 March 2006 in a BPL family.\n1. A girl must have completed the eighth grade to be eligible for the maturity amount\n1. She cannot have been married off before turning 18 years old.\n\n",
